column1: 356,CAP'N CRUNCH® Original Cereal,"Sweet and golden, with a crunch you’ll love, nothing competes with the original Cap’n Crunch® cereal. Grab a bowl or cup for an easy snack that goes great with couch time, anytime.

","INGREDIENTS: CORN FLOUR, SUGAR, OAT FLOUR, BROWN SUGAR, COCONUT OIL, SALT, COLOUR, BHT (PRESERVATIVE).VITAMINS AND MINERALS: IRON, NIACINAMIDE, THIAMINE MONONITRATE (VITAMIN B1), CALCIUM PANTOTHENATE, PYRIDOXINE HYDROCHLORIDE (VITAMIN B6), FOLIC ACID.",ClassicBI.png,ClassicBI.png,,Per 1 cup (30 g),"- Calories

399,CAP’N CRUNCH’S CRUNCH BERRIES<sup>TM</sup> flavour cereal,"Rock your taste buds in a berry crunchy way. Cap’n Crunch’s Crunch Berries™ flavour cereal takes the original crunch you love, and adds in bursts of colourful berry flavour. Grab a bowl or cup for an easy snack that goes great with couch time, anytime.

","Ingredients: Sugars (sugar, brown sugar), Corn flour, Oat flour, Coconut oil, Salt, Sodium citrate, Malic acid, BHT (preservative), Tartrazine, Allura red, Brilliant blue FCF, Sunset yellow FCF, Natural and artificial flavour.
Vitamins and minerals: Iron, Niacinamide, Thiamine mononitrate (vitamin B1), Calcium pantothenate, Pyridoxine hydrochloride (vitamin B6), Folic acid.

378,CAP'N CRUNCH'S CANUCK CRUNCH<sup>TM</sup> Cereal ,"Cap'n Crunch's Canuck CrunchTM cereal takes the crunch you love, and adds in red berries for a Canadian themed bowl of fun. This cereal will add an extra splash  to your July 1st celebrations. Grab a bowl or cup to add some fun to breakfast time or snack time! Available for a limited time only.","INGREDIENTS: CORN FLOUR, SUGAR, OAT FLOUR, BROWN SUGAR, COCONUT OIL, SALT, SODIUM CITRATE, MALIC ACID, BHT (PRESERVATIVE), COLOUR, NATURAL AND ARTIFICIAL FLAVOUR. VITAMINS AND MINERALS: IRON, THIAMINE MONONITRATE (VITAMIN B1), NIACINAMIDE, CALCIUM PANTOTHENATE, PYRIDOXINE HYDROCHLORIDE (VITAMIN B6), FOLIC ACID.
